name: h i g h s c o r e 9 9 9 9
description: highscore 9999 came out of a field of pure brazilian 90s nostalgia, when me and friends used to play dk2 and smw on the snes in each others houses and pretend we were link playing the ocarina at grandmother's house on sunday afternoons. then i proceed to discuss this past nostalgias today. who are we now? what still remains in our hearts as grown ups?
